Package: nids-ipv6-config
Version: 1.0.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: DevOps Team <devops@example.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9)
Homepage: https://github.com/your-org/nids-ipv6-config
Description: Network Intrusion Detection System IPv6 Configuration Application
 A configuration application for managing Network Intrusion Detection System
 (NIDS) IPv6 settings on Ubuntu 22.04 LTS and Red Hat 9.6 systems.
 Provides command-line interface for IPv6 mode capability configuration,
 monitoring enablement, traffic rules management, and comprehensive logging.